data.description: Step into your new haven with this coveted end unit townhome. Offering a 3-bedroom/2.5-bath floorplan with a 1-car garage, all bedrooms are conveniently situated upstairs. The home has undergone renovations, presenting a turnkey condition with a charming appeal. Enjoy the freshness of new laminate flooring on the first floor and the added perk of no rear neighbors in this meticulously cared-for residence. Nestled next to a cul de sac, the location ensures tranquility with pets warmly welcomed. Within minutes, discover the convenience of Costco, shopping, malls, restaurants, places of worship, a water park, and more. Plus, relish the top-rated education at Everglades Elementary, an ''A''-rated school. Welcome home!
